"Except" list. This is a noun list that can contain anything that's in a regular noun list plus some things that only make sense as exceptions, such as possessive nouns (e.g., "mine"). `grammar `[`exceptList`](../object/exceptList.html)`(single)`` :   `[`ExceptListProd`](../object/ExceptListProd.html)
